<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>StudyHub - High School Study Material</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f5f7fb;
}

header{
    background:#2563eb;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
    text-align:center;
}

nav{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:20px;
    background:#1e40af;
    padding:12px;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
    text-align:center;
    padding:60px 20px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:42px;
    color:#2563eb;
}

.hero p{
    margin-top:15px;
    color:#555;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    background:#2563eb;
    color:white;
    border-radius:8px;
    text-decoration:none;
}

.container{
    width:90%;
    max-width:1100px;
    margin:auto;
}

.cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
    margin:40px 0;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

.card h3{
    color:#2563eb;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

footer{
    background:#1e293b;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    margin-top:40px;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>StudyHub</h1>
<p>Free Study Material for High School Students</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Notes</a>
<a href="#">Question Papers</a>
<a href="#">MCQs</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
<h1>Study Smart. Score Better.</h1>
<p>Free Notes, Sample Papers, MCQs and Revision Material for Class 9 & 10.</p>

<a href="#" class="btn">Explore Notes</a>
</section>

<div class="container">

<div class="cards">

<div class="card">
<h3>📘 Science</h3>
<p>Chapter-wise notes, diagrams, formulas and important questions.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📗 Mathematics</h3>
<p>NCERT solutions, formulas, examples and practice worksheets.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📙 English</h3>
<p>Grammar, writing skills, literature summaries and vocabulary.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📕 Social Science</h3>
<p>History, Geography, Civics and Economics revision notes.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>📝 Previous Papers</h3>
<p>Download previous year question papers with solutions.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🎯 Daily Quiz</h3>
<p>Practice MCQs and improve your exam preparation.</p>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 StudyHub | Made for High School Students</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>